## Orders API

* Order Cancellation

Example Usage:

    Order order = new Order();  
    order.setId("10001");  
    order.setToken("vHgYNS7dbotHjziuPCZQ");  
    order.setComment("10000 ko cancel");  
    order.setDue_date(new GregorianCalendar(2012, 02, 28));  
    Response response = order.cancel();  

* Order Rescheduling

